<p>In the latest development, French investigators arrested five more people in connection with the October 19 theft of crown jewels from the Louvre, bringing the number of suspects held to seven, but none of the precious items have been recovered . Prosecutor Laure Beccuau said two earlier detainees have &quot;partially&quot; admitted involvement and face preliminary charges including theft and criminal conspiracy, while detectives traced leads through DNA found on an abandoned scooter and at the scene . Authorities say the pieces — historic jewels once belonging to France&#x27;s royal and imperial families and valued at about €88m (roughly $102m) — were taken from the Louvre&#x27;s Apollo gallery in daylight, and investigators continue focused searches around Paris and the suburbs .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/QErPtgEuF24c1v8_BjF1giA_r3pogDwR8sPVnoWo9yHF2fnNK_F9Hph9uw2Rvsrxw5H1BZWjEwWsly_c6EgcTVgxztL9eidt9FS4PPjcuDjSiqa9IiXSIsX-ZAOdvDt-omsG3gCgssOGYZrNCG5xNbGuOWAC_ZVRpu_HugAo2nKoYkb7sm1LNAwkgKqPKlor0Y4LVYhaYYI4j7NuASfzMOYKL2HgGwzmb53B4JYfcH1XfTgeID-4B5u-ib-NSG5ZQkBNuInNkLpVarK58Q' alt='Paris prosecutor Laure Beccuau and police officials at a news conference about the Louvre jewel investigation.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>DNA leads: Investigators linked two earlier suspects to the scene through DNA traces found on an abandoned scooter and on the broken window, prompting arrests and charges .</li><li>Airport arrest: One of the first two suspects was detained at Paris-Charles de Gaulle airport while attempting to board a one-way flight to Algeria, police said .</li><li>Sentence incentives: The prosecutor said judicial authorities would consider reducing sentences if the stolen jewels are returned, a factor potentially influencing suspects&#x27; decisions .</li><li>Parliament scrutiny: A culture committee roundtable in the Sénat highlighted outdated perimeter cameras at French museums and called for a comprehensive security upgrade plan .</li></ul><blockquote>Will take that into account - Laure Beccuau</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Paris public prosecutor (Laure Beccuau): The arrests were made in and around Paris, and two earlier detainees have partially admitted involvement while investigators continue searching for the missing goods. (<a href='https://www.politico.eu/article/5-more-suspects-arrested-connection-with-louvre-heist/'>Politico Europe</a>)</li><li>French culture committee (Sénat): A roundtable flagged outdated surveillance camera systems at the Louvre and called for a coordinated security response across museums. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/culture/article/2025/10/29/french-museums-security-under-scrutiny-in-the-senat-after-louvre-heist_6746906_30.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.ft.com/content/aa74f8bd-75f3-40da-9602-da3a782cef22'>Five more arrested over €88mn Louvre royal jewel heist</a> - ft.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/louvre-jewels-heist-5-more-arrests-gems-still-missing/'>5 more arrests in brazen Louvre crown jewels heist but gems still missing</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.politico.eu/article/5-more-suspects-arrested-connection-with-louvre-heist/'>5 more suspects arrested in connection with Louvre heist</a> - politico.eu</li><li><a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-10-30/five-new-suspects-arrested-over-louvre-museum-jewels-robbery/105954530'>Five new suspects arrested over Louvre heist, Paris prosecutor says</a> - abc.net.au</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/oct/30/suspects-arrested-louvre-robbery-paris-crown-jewels'>Five new suspects arrested in connection with Louvre robbery</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/paris-prosecutor-says-2-suspects-partially-admitted-participation-in-louvre-jewel-heist'>Paris prosecutor says 2 suspects ‘partially’ admitted participation in Louvre jewel heist</a> - pbs.org</li><li><a href='https://